title: What PRS can I find at the guitar center that sounds and feels like the PRS SE? - Quora

response.answer_text: PRS SE models are Korean made versions of popular PRS American made guitars. If you are referring to the PRS SE guitar with P-90 pickups, it was recently discontinued. I recently pickuped up a PRS SE Mark Tremonti Custom with hard case for a very reasonable price. It is an excellent reproduction of the American PRS Mark Tremonti, but has different pickups.
